{"tid":998870,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"中意左兩個男仔","createTime":"2019-01-28T09:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T10:13:41.000Z","uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2d80e48f7054c575183d6b100b9b4fec908058d0","tid":998870,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"喜歡了兩個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司一齊做嘢<br />\n一個肥矮<br />\n一個高瘦<br />\n兩個都唔係靚仔<br />\n但感覺舒服合眼緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家可能話選擇好明顯<br />\n如果係咁明顯就唔洗請教大家啦<br />\n肥仔好單純、直接，有d可愛，不過就讀書唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘦仔讀過大學，個人醒目，但有時候想引人注意的小動作多左d，感覺亦機心比較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我其實識瘦仔先<br />\n喜歡瘦仔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但懷疑瘦仔有女朋友<br />\n唔想做第三者<br />\n同埋有諗過<br />\n如果我同瘦仔<br />\n我會唔捨得肥仔唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但對著肥仔有對牛彈琴嘅感覺<br />\n唔知大家點睇<br />\n（唔好問家底、錢唔係重要因素）"},{"pid":"d588a2b63698c34f18a138686fa570220e041e41","tid":998870,"uid":198783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079d9c009de4b6f49cf553b29df8aad51f3b2ce8","tid":998870,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"利申:真絲非gay"},{"pid":"4544e560b5bd50a08b0d4b302a712ad6b04c9b71","tid":998870,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:53:21.000Z","msg":"嘩 三碌jer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b6049bd809a85bf509ed8502719e828b5d2c162","tid":998870,"uid":34935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"假膠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/998857/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihk